	<Text>You can issue multiple commands to a unit or group of units to be executed by holding the &lt;color=FFCFCF00&gt;&apos;SHIFT&apos;&lt;color=FFCFCFCF&gt; key down when giving the orders.  When finished, release the &lt;color=FFCFCF00&gt;&apos;SHIFT&lt;color=FFCFCFCF&gt; key and the orders will be carried out in the order that they were given.
Light tanks and AFVs can patrol area. To order unit to patrol select it and click &quot;Patrol&quot; button (blinking), then click points to patrol while holding &lt;color=FFCFCF00&gt;&apos;SHIFT&apos;&lt;color=FFCFCFCF&gt; key.
Select M3 Stuart tank and order it to patrol some area.</Text>
